 {"id":"bd-mblr.1.3","title":"Critical-Path Coverage Gap Report","description":"Define critical correctness/safety paths (MVCC conflict detection, WAL replay, pager checkpointing, transaction lifecycle, schema ops, recovery) and map current test coverage + realism to each path. Deliver prioritized missing-case backlog with risk ranking.","design":"Model invariant -> evidence mapping explicitly so changes can be diffed and reviewed over time.","acceptance_criteria":"- Critical invariant set is enumerated and linked to concrete tests/coverage evidence.
- Gap report ranks missing or weakly-covered invariants by risk and blast radius.
